column5: OK I've been dealing with making prints and so I've gone through the library and brought everything up to "Print worthy"---very much a pain in the  Anyway a lot may remember a version of this one----just finished---I'm leavin it alone now.
I've said it before and say it again.....  you got mad skills with the brush Terry Awesome job dude!!!
Thanks Jacques---and all's it took was a lifetime
Very nice work bushart. I have to say that your paintings look a lot like some of Vincent Van Gogh's work. Very nice indeed!! I wish I could paint.  Keep up the good work. Stan
Thank you very much Stan---I really don't know what to say with a compliment such as this.  Thank You
I am a proud owner of one of Terrance's canvas's  it is simply beautiful!  and this one I am sure is equally as impressive  looking awesome from here! and I know even better better in real life.  G.
it's a real good looking painting but don't cut your ear off.....no matter what they say .....
Mighty fine brushwork you have.Hopefully one day I will have one of your masterpeices. Excelent work indeed.
Thanks Terry----cut ear off---don't think so----wife votes for having mouth sewn shut though  Thanks Vinnimon
Nice work there Mr. O'Conner! You are very prolific with the art work. Gonna try oil painting fishes when i have the time. Inspiring stuff
